{"tid":1309380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喂！五大訴求呢？食懞你地呀？","createTime":"2019-07-12T07:26:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T14:31:53.000Z","uid":63822,"like":6,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d6bff9a6a49b04bb5a9a6bd354c6d711c2b4c7d2","tid":1309380,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:26:23.000Z","msg":"吉野家又好連儂牆又好，洗唔洗all in落去玩呀<br />\n政府而家唔出聲，件事慢慢變成商警民矛盾，政府好似事不關己咁啦<br />\n死線呢？行動升級呢？<br />\n唔好唔記得我地死左5個，五大訴求完成度係0%<br />\n有精力有限，繼續玩落去玩謝哂自己人，到真係環背水一戰就會因為唔夠人失敗<br />\n環講幾多次雨傘教訓先識醒呀<br />\n係你地全城聚焦吉野家連儂牆既時候，監控柱已經慢慢出緊街啦<br />\n我地由-5分變到-7分啦，點解仲可以咁樂觀<br />\n尋日梁烈士先出殯，比佢見到佢既死換來係-5變-7，你地良心過唔過得去<br />\n<br />\n繼續玩支線，一世都唔洗旨意爆機"},{"pid":"c702d32850f72c58287d579fa20abbbbc7b45348","tid":1309380,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:27:27.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"b17ea5aad8cf25d507f927fa457d897962f1c5fc","tid":1309380,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:30:48.000Z","msg":"如果罷買同連儂牆可以令政府跪低，我地2014已經有雙普選啦"},{"pid":"b21378e4e33b2c3bbb2a0100962ab0a22791e57b","tid":1309380,"uid":12675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:33:11.000Z","msg":"<code>長期爭戰 兄弟爬山 各有各做 不分化 不割蓆</code>"},{"pid":"db4062d770c31fe08577676bb19fa5a479c1404d","tid":1309380,"uid":63822,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:33:56.000Z","msg":"日日出去守牆，好撚攰好撚消耗意志<br />\n我地有幾多精神可以比你玩<br />\n連儂牆洗唔洗日日吹雞要人要人呀<br />\n打游擊，人地撕咪由佢，第二日撕一貼百囉<br />\n連儂牆就日日吹哂雞死守<br />\n佔立會果陣就記者多過夢遊人<br />\n係唔係搞撚錯哂呀"},{"pid":"c5f0174ff60ce580d81047a1e2d3c80fa2aeecb4","tid":1309380,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:44:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75e12d66b4e26a58d3e82529f245798ea8b93bf0","tid":1309380,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:44:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f22a2e67d73b8a7e581e6f5ebfbd7ccefdf9e1ec","tid":1309380,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:44:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14abe1f3333f221949eaa09248cbc99d626d9ec1","tid":1309380,"uid":117892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:45:08.000Z","msg":"比起任何事 我只求每個義士平安歸隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304296</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n釋放所有被捕示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成立獨立調查委員會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推到有更多被捕示威者嘅消息為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JWt95h0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJWt95h0.png&h=5793562a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4wy6n4G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4wy6n4G.png&h=bb495966&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7a73a2ca12c4d8f71339047764c8c695caa3e10","tid":1309380,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:45:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86166cdd802c43a0240fa8d073b4c2a26ada3c9d","tid":1309380,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:57:04.000Z","msg":"負皮既討論下<br />\n係唔係5大訴求烈士遺志並不重要<br />\n最重要係消耗大家意志抵制呢個光復嗰個？<br />\n聽日既光復我都會去，但心態已經唔係當初發夢果陣覺得會贏，有希望，有鬥志<br />\n純粹係覺得weekend冇野做，咪幫下手囉<br />\n我唔知係唔係得我心態轉差左<br />\n但咁磨落去一定愈來愈多人疲倦，愈來愈少人出<br />\n我都唔知我會唔會有一日覺得<br />\n「日撚日都話要人，5大訴求離我地愈來愈遠<br />\n出去有撚用咩！」"},{"pid":"3cd7f9d2061e09334f9085f490ce355153e97798","tid":1309380,"uid":279004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:03:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29ee94ee1d41f27e845590d4c8c339fde267b300","tid":1309380,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:16:32.000Z","msg":"你地要人要人既時候，林鄭已被放生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18c6ad0ef46f05ed039c1dc86cc384b18acac123","tid":130938